<h4>MISSION</h4>
<p>
    We're an organisation promoting a healthier community by providing you a platform
    with resources to aid smokers in their efforts to quit smoking. There will be
    articles posted by certified doctors about smoking and its risks. Smokers are able
    comment on these articles and interact with one another. Similarly, smokers will
    also be able to share their own recovery stories.
</p>

<p>
